      • setLookupsToDiscover

        public void setLookupsToDiscover(String[] groups,
                                 net.jini.core.discovery.LookupLocator[] locators)
        This method should be called whenever the groups and/or locators this regInfo is supposed to discover are changed during a test. This method examines the new groups and locators to discover and then re-sets the values of the fields in this class that related to the expected discovery/discard state of this regInfo.
